OL,3,C#13.5m for businesses and workers
OL,4,Caffected by Tata blast furnace closure
OL,6,F#13.5 million in funding is being
OL,7,Freleased to support supply chain
OL,8,Fbusinesses and workers affected by
OL,9,FTata Steel's decarbonisation plans at
OL,10,Fits Port Talbot site, the UK
OL,11,FGovernment will announce on Thursday.
OL,13,FIt's the first release of money from
OL,14,Fthe Tata Steel / Port Talbot
OL,15,FTransition Board fund.
OL,17,FWelsh Secretary Jo Stevens MP is set
OL,18,Fto make the announcement today (15
OL,19,FAugust) at her second meeting as chair
OL,20,Fof the Board.
