OL,3,C#13.5m for businesses and workers
OL,4,Caffected by Tata blast furnace closure
OL,6,FThousands of jobs in the town will be
OL,7,Fcut later this year when Tata steel is
OL,8,Fset to close the second of its Port
OL,9,FTalbot blast furnaces in September due
OL,10,Fto accumulating losses of #1m a day.
OL,12,FPlans are in place to build an
OL,13,Felectric arc furnace at the Port
OL,14,FTalbot site, which will be able to
OL,15,Fproduce greener steel.
OL,17,FTata says it has ambitions to produce
OL,18,Fnet-zero steel by 2045 in the UK "at
OL,19,Fthe latest" and plans to reduce 30% of
OL,20,Fits CO2 emissions by 2030.
