OL,3,C#13.5m for businesses and workers
OL,4,Caffected by Tata blast furnace closure
OL,6,FThe UK Government says it will support
OL,7,Flocal businesses that are heavily
OL,8,Freliant on Tata Steel as their primary
OL,9,Fcustomer.
OL,11,FIt adds it will allow them to turn
OL,12,Ftowards new markets and customers
OL,13,Fwhere necessary.
OL,15,FMoney will also be available to
OL,16,Fworkers affected by the transition to
OL,17,Fhelp them to find new jobs, access
OL,18,Ftraining and gain skills and
OL,19,Fqualifications in areas where there
OL,20,Fare vacancies, the UK government has
OL,21,Fsaid.
