OL,6,FThe Welsh Secretary is also set to
OL,7,Fannounce that over 50 businesses have
OL,8,Fsigned a pledge to support any workers
OL,9,Fforced to leave their jobs in the
OL,10,Fsteelworks.
OL,12,FThe businesses, which include Fintech
OL,13,FWales, The Royal Mint, Cardiff
OL,14,FMetropolitan University, RWE Energy,
OL,15,FLedwood Mechanical Engineering and Pro
OL,16,FSteel Engineering, are said to have
OL,17,Fcommitted practical support for
OL,18,Fworkers ranging from guaranteed
OL,19,Finterviews for anyone made redundant,
OL,20,Fto providing training and coaching.
