OL,7,FNational Officer for Steel Alun Davies
OL,8,Fsaid: "We welcome this announcement,
OL,9,Fwhich demonstrates that the UK Labour
OL,10,FGovernment is stepping up to provide
OL,11,Fsupport both to workers affected by
OL,12,FTata's decarbonisation plans, and to
OL,13,Fthe wider community in and around Port
OL,14,FTalbot.
OL,16,F"The Welsh Secretary Jo Stevens has
OL,17,Facted at pace to ensure that this
OL,18,Ffirst tranche of funding can be
OL,19,Freleased as swiftly as possible, and
OL,20,Fwe thank her for her steadfast
OL,21,Fcommitment to our steel communities.
